snippet.title: PAC-MAN Championship Edition DX - PS3 / X360 - Trailer
snippet.description:
▲ Pac-Man CEDX is now half price on Xbox Live® Arcade in Europe ! If you haven't already (and why haven't you?), now is the time to get your hands on one of the best arcade games of all times. Be quick, this offer runs till the 8th of March only ! ▲

You've never seen PAC-MAN quite like this!

PAC-MAN Championship Edition DX will be available on PSN and X360 Live Arcade, November 24 2010.

For more information, check your local http://www.namcobandaigames.eu
